</BULLET>
<BULLET><PARAGRAPH><LAUNCHWORD APP="/usr/sbin/nr" PARMS="http://www.telstra.com.au/info/security.html">http://www.telstra.com.au/info/security.html</LAUNCHWORD>
&mdash;Many links to general network security information including security-related mailing lists.</PARAGRAPH>
</BULLET>
<BULLET><PARAGRAPH><LAUNCHWORD APP="/usr/sbin/nr" PARMS="http://www.cert.org/">http://www.cert.org/</LAUNCHWORD>
&mdash;The Computer Emergency Response Team (CERT) Coordination Center was established by the Advanced Research Projects Agency to coordinate information regarding security threats to the Internet.</PARAGRAPH>
