&mdash;A collection of UNIX security FAQs.</PARAGRAPH>
</BULLET>
<BULLET><PARAGRAPH><LAUNCHWORD APP="/usr/sbin/nr" PARMS="http://www-ns.rutgers.edu/www-security/index.html">http://www-ns.rutgers.edu/www-security/index.html</LAUNCHWORD>
